(numIntPhysRegisters, nICacheWays).explanation: The number of integer physical registers and instruction cache associativity are independent architectural parameters that serve different functions in the processor pipeline;

(numIntPhysRegisters, enableSFBOpt).explanation: Store forwarding buffer optimization is a memory subsystem feature that operates independently of the integer register file size;

(numIntPhysRegisters, nDCacheTLBWays).explanation: Data cache TLB associativity and integer register file size are independent architectural parameters serving different pipeline stages;
